item.title: Roneka Patterson
item.description: These past two years have been stressful for all of us in a lot of ways, but this week’s guest is proof that you can find a way to redirect those feelings into something positive. Meet Roneka Patterson, an associate creative director at Hawkeye in Dallas, Texas, and the co-creator of The Unwritten Rules. Roneka and I talked about adjusting to work from home life, and she shared a bit about her process and what it’s like to be a creative director... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/YDtGA1K7
